{"author":"RebarBotNava","data":{"alias":"resting-feudalist-screamer","description":"## Reproduction Steps\n1. Land commit 10837ca88 (adds external volume gerrit_reviewbot_tickets to infra/compose/docker-compose.yml) WITHOUT updating the provisioning loops in infra/scripts/compose-up.sh.\n2. Every rebar-autodeploy tick that sees a new main SHA rebuilds the review-bot image, then `docker compose up -d review-bot` aborts: external volume \"gerrit_reviewbot_tickets\" not found. Backoff resets on each new main SHA, so a busy push day compresses many multi-GB docker builds into a tight window.\n3. Around 2026-07-10 03:15–03:52 UTC the 30G root disk transiently filled (pip Errno 28 in the autodeploy builds, journal); concurrent review clones then failed (VOTER_ERROR \"No space left on device\"), fail-closing changes 452/461/462 with [LLM-Review: BLOCK — coverage-gap (review-error)].\n\n**Expected:** autodeploy converges after every main advance; reviews never veto for infra reasons.\n**Actual:** deploys failed on every attempt for ~41h (fail #21 by Jul 10 00:00); transient ENOSPC fail-closed live reviews.\n\n## Resolution (applied on-box 2026-07-10 ~04:45 UTC, supervised)\n- Pruned builder/image caches (~3.5G), verified RED via `docker compose up -d --dry-run review-bot` (reproduced the volume error).\n- Created the missing bind volume exactly matching sibling spec: `docker volume create --driver local --opt type=none --opt o=bind --opt device=/var/gerrit/site/reviewbot-tickets gerrit_reviewbot_tickets` (+ mkdir of host dir); dry-run then GREEN.\n- One supervised autodeploy run: \"review-bot redeployed + healthy\", deployed-sha now d1e4cd5c; Gerrit container untouched; disk 20% used.\n- The repo-side fix for infra/scripts/compose-up.sh (and hardening) is child/discovered work.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] Autodeploy converges (deploy complete) after volume creation; no bot-build-failed since.\n- [ ] Review-bot posts a real (non-coverage-gap) LLM-Review vote post-deploy (functional probe on change 461).\n- [ ] Stale coverage-gap veto on change 452 cleared via /rerun.\n- [ ] Discovered follow-up defects filed and linked discovered_from this ticket.","id":"2731-4c53-56b4-46cc","parent_id":"","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"bug","title":"incident: review-bot fail-closed LLM-Review vetoes — root disk exhaustion from a 41h autodeploy failure loop (missing gerrit_reviewbot_tickets volume)"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1783658922300790001,"uuid":"08e12b96-959a-4d81-8c2d-468572927fbb"}